query:
DELETE FROM island_guides
WHERE contentType = 'island' AND placeId IS NOT NULL AND id NOT IN (
  SELECT MIN(id) FROM (
    SELECT MIN(id) as id
    FROM island_guides
    WHERE contentType = 'island' AND placeId IS NOT NULL
    GROUP BY placeId
  ) as keep_ids
)
